{
  "stem": "5795.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, I don't know where they got it from in his book-- I've got a copy of the-- of his book there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I was warned, don't give them more than the official ration.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I thought I was doing them harm when they kept on shouting, hunger, [NON-ENGLISH] hunger, hunger!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "When a kid asks and he cried hunger, you can't-- you can't say no straight away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] So I fed them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this Derek--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was an average of about 12,000. 12,000 were dead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Between 10,000 or 12,000 were dead, and there must have been about 6,000 or 8,000 alive-- no more, more. 13,000 died after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was 10,000 to 15,000 dead when we came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 13,000 died after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So there must have been many, many thousand.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then a Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Meiklejohn. ?] He was famous for his Bengal Famine Mixture, the British government sent him out to Bengal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he came to me, and he said, padre, they're not eating my food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, forgive me, sir, what I'm going to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You've never had this experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What do you mean?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I've just-- I've been-- just come back from Bengal.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, let me try to explain myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When a person's upset, a businessmen, something upsets him, the secretary, or his partners, or his customers, the gastric juices don't appear to be in-- in order.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he'll come home and his wife will plate something in front of him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't eat that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Or she gives him something, it gives him pains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's about when you're upset, it ups the acid, and these people were upset.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can imagine.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How can they-- Yes, I see that.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
